            "title": "北角英皇道行人路現危險招牌 警方消防封路清拆",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"北角英皇道行人路現危險招牌 警方消防封路清拆\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ed04d3fa18ace03ad1033b3509822297/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031423291522079.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">北角英皇道行人路現危險招牌 警方消防封路清拆</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（3月14日）晚上10時半左右，北角英皇道195號，一塊約3米長、離地約2米高、橫跨行人路的招牌搖搖欲墜。警方消防到場後，封鎖現場一段行人路並將危險廣告牌清拆。事件中無人受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4138354/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防先行清拆廣告牌較危險部份。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e746fab4610bccee3d2efa742b0b5a5/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_231815157.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防先行清拆廣告牌較危險部份。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4138353/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防檢查廣告牌其餘部份是否安全，警方協助封路避免途人接近。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9fe749cf80f8be7a6a2062077628febc/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_231817018.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防檢查廣告牌其餘部份是否安全，警方協助封路避免途人接近。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
