            "title": "空手道超聯第2站｜「世一」劉幕裳杭州不失一局入決賽",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1c4258bd0621060696037805258c7e8c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031423032850005.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港空手道「世一」形女劉慕裳（Grace）周五在杭州舉行的WKF K1 超級聯賽第2站，再次以不失一局闖入周日決賽，繼1月巴黎站後再跟世界排名第2的日本對手尾野真步在決賽碰頭，港將力圖爭取2025年首冠。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉慕裳周日再跟日本宿敵爭冠。WKF圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/00083ae14956f6e00edec7b79a6a5157/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_10_48_42_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉慕裳周日再跟日本宿敵爭冠。WKF圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"WKF圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/690ba0256801be8a12ae5ce28890404f/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_10_48_07_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        WKF圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>今站杭州站是新一個賽季的第2站，共有30位來自世界各地的「形女」參賽，一如以往先進行分組賽，Grace沒受到考驗，先以41.9:40.60勝伊朗37歲老將Mahsa Afsaneh，再以42:39.8勝德國應屆歐錦賽銅牌得主Jasmin Juettner，強勢躋身8強（8強中有4位來自日本，其中3人入準決賽）。\n\n</p>\n<p>應屆亞洲冠軍的Grace在半準決賽對另一位伊朗選手、去年亞錦賽銅牌得主Fatemeh Sadeghi，Grace以43.30:41.60躋身4強，對日本的東佐江子，這正是1月法國站的4強翻版，勝方同樣是Grace，她以43.70:42.60勝出入周日決賽。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"尾野真步。WKF圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b99642abb3d6724af565180da06a78c2/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_10_48_32_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尾野真步。WKF圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>決賽是第一站法國的翻版，亦是去年9月亞錦賽的決賽同一對手、日本的尾野真步，在這2戰中，各取得1勝，周日決戰，有望報上仗一箭之仇。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：徐嘉華\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058232/即時-體育-空手道超聯第2站-世一-劉幕裳杭州不失一局入決賽",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 23:21:15",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黃子佼買逾二千部未成年性影像毫無悔意！台灣命理師爆其「惡業大爆發」 超慘下場曝光",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黃子佼買逾二千部未成年性影像毫無悔意！台灣命理師爆其「惡業大爆發」 超慘下場曝光\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e6f83774a9c08536e8f4a598c627cc8e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031422494581182.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黃子佼買逾二千部未成年性影像毫無悔意！台灣命理師爆其「惡業大爆發」 超慘下場曝光</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>藝人黃子佼從專門販售違法性影像的「創意私房」論壇，購買並持有高達2259部未成年性影像，一審判處8個月有期徒刑，不予緩刑。黃子佼日前被拍到一家三口幸福天倫同遊，引發眾怒，網傳黃子佼去年在臉書上的道歉文疑似為復出試水溫。對此，命理師沈嶸直指黃子佼惡業大爆發，超慘下場曝光。\n\n</p><h2>黃子佼充斥不良業力</h2>\n<p>命理師沈嶸對此表示，過去曾通靈調閱因果簿發現黃子佼有「自毀前程」、「死不認錯」、「狡辯」、「欺騙」、「性侵」、「冷血」、「無動於衷」、「狡滑」、「情色上癮」等眾多不良業力。黃子佼多次在聲明稿中表達悔意，但他在審理過程中卻說出「我看不出來這些人是不是小朋友」、「論壇上的標題都很模糊」、「我不知道買的是什麼東西」等避重就輕的說詞。\n\n</p><h2>黃子佼沒有懺悔決心</h2>\n<p>沈嶸直言，黃子佼的行為完全體現了他的不良業力「狡辯」、「欺騙」、「死不認錯」，與通靈結果完全吻合。判決書中更寫到，黃子佼並未與這些受害者達成和解，至今也未向受害者做出正式的道歉與補償，而且還被發現疑似透過公關公司購買大量網軍帳號，由此可見「無動於衷」、「狡猾」的業力，讓黃子佼至今仍看不出他懺悔的決心。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3435817/%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E4%BD%BC%E6%8D%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8D%E9%9B%85%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6-%E8%99%95%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8D%E7%B4%AF%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%BE%A9%E5%87%BA-%E8%BC%BF%E8%AB%96%E9%9C%87%E6%80%92%E6%80%A8%E5%85%B6%E5%A6%BB%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB\">黃子佼捲未成年不雅影片案件 處心積累部署復出 輿論震怒怨其妻維護丈夫</a>\n</p><h2>黃子佼捲性醜聞：</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677997/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼是台灣著名主持。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31c285432ab42133dec703073c9e6cd4/2023-06/mickey1972330_352692255_814062933407549_5674871022077263737_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼是台灣著名主持。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2678067/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼的恩師為台灣殿堂級主持張小燕。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7599ba94a83decae34d849effb0f9904/2023-06/W12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼的恩師為台灣殿堂級主持張小燕。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677999/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼在兩岸都有大量主持工作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3eb55fd1f151e2a12665f56f43752c33/2023-06/mickey1972330_355121290_818701849610324_253678741650218370_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼在兩岸都有大量主持工作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2678066/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼口才好反應快，在台灣主持界很吃香。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/246fd5acc498964b350b6f8502e91243/2023-06/W11_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼口才好反應快，在台灣主持界很吃香。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677989/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼與年輕20歲的太太孟耿如，去年誕下一女。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b119902c0d5fab59b9aab8f1570dadfa/2023-06/mickey1972330_334797722_1329509004570156_4185827960718225324_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼與年輕20歲的太太孟耿如，去年誕下一女。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677895/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網紅「和我一起．走在法國的365天」的Zofia，去年發長文透露被性騷擾詳情。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6e0425ce67c1a0fc5d1b725488a463f/2023-06/c86edd40-0e52-11ee-babf-bd8451f0be68.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網紅「和我一起．走在法國的365天」的Zofia，去年發長文透露被性騷擾詳情。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2678205/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼在Facebook直播中道歉。  ​\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6d4258dbf7f24239e12cc57723c4a320/2023-06/VideoScreenshot--Facebook-0_23__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼在Facebook直播中道歉。  ​\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4138325/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"命理師沈嶸（左）表示黃子佼（右）有「死不認錯」、「狡辯」等不良業力。（TVBS新聞網圖片）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d27c902375b6b439fb520a1634388dba/2025-03/1312312.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        命理師沈嶸（左）表示黃子佼（右）有「死不認錯」、「狡辯」等不良業力。（TVBS新聞網圖片）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2789012/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼點名10多位藝人，爆料演藝圈黑幕。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2e6b08f6719334e6a16fa3f8e91444a7/2023-08/wong_4_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼點名10多位藝人，爆料演藝圈黑幕。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2678001/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有台媒報道黃子佼酒後情緒不穩，揮刀自殘需緊急送醫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d5d75e045eed844b4e446a2b39d2d33/2023-06/VideoScreenshot--3-1_10_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有台媒報道黃子佼酒後情緒不穩，揮刀自殘需緊急送醫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3246186/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼針對十多年前的「失禮」行為向網紅道歉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0940f97aff218c24b082b98f9b9004fc/2024-02/HUANG_03.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼針對十多年前的「失禮」行為向網紅道歉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3246187/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網紅Zofia晚間也在社交網發文，配上藍天燦爛笑容，疑對黃子佼道歉作出回應。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/985615a007dfa54870f371859cd7604c/2024-02/HUANG_04.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網紅Zofia晚間也在社交網發文，配上藍天燦爛笑容，疑對黃子佼道歉作出回應。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4126913/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼積極部署復出，惹來台灣輿論震怒。（TVBS新聞網圖片）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a8b8bb4bd33adf2ea66ab93a80dce935/2025-03/VV2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼積極部署復出，惹來台灣輿論震怒。（TVBS新聞網圖片）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3246188/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網紅Zofia留言：「相信只看着未來和遠方，良善待人、努力生活，會越來越好的，也衷心期盼孩子們未來的世界會有更多美好。」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24cd42f7178d3ba1f8e814007e6c7991/2024-02/HUANG_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網紅Zofia留言：「相信只看着未來和遠方，良善待人、努力生活，會越來越好的，也衷心期盼孩子們未來的世界會有更多美好。」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3246189/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網紅Zofia的經紀人也說洽談和解，唯一訴求就是公開誠心誠意的道歉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4acd330726b7f17f3559fcca843e152/2024-02/HUANG_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網紅Zofia的經紀人也說洽談和解，唯一訴求就是公開誠心誠意的道歉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3246190/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼太太孟耿如亦於社交網回應：「勇敢面對，平靜生活。」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c91811070a53153c913e21dd7671f8f0/2024-02/HUANG_07.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼太太孟耿如亦於社交網回應：「勇敢面對，平靜生活。」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/3246191/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"孟耿如對老公黃子佼百分百支持。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f523bb0c5886ea456e365d871d8293c8/2024-02/HUANG_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        孟耿如對老公黃子佼百分百支持。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677990/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Metoo事件曝光後，黃子佼好爸爸的人設崩壞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/15dbe9b85d7b08da4d05df3bacdec37e/2023-06/mickey1972330_338133746_739377097844003_9046294155412708987_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Metoo事件曝光後，黃子佼好爸爸的人設崩壞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677991/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼好爸爸的人設崩壞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb85e703f026421348e30e28e4088571/2023-06/mickey1972330_339424455_885447792527380_1388004627278202066_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼好爸爸的人設崩壞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677992/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼與孟耿如人前表現恩愛。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/58de0d48b9157d89d4ec907eb3eccbe4/2023-06/mickey1972330_339578846_619732572903696_853168552388341087_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼與孟耿如人前表現恩愛。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677993/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"經常將女兒掛在嘴邊。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3d3a4827cfbfa8d732f15c336eaada9f/2023-06/mickey1972330_339791185_761391145555321_3605753416450001159_n%20%281%29.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        經常將女兒掛在嘴邊。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677994/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"孟耿如2020年嫁給黃子佼。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82a2f586346837e048228a56e4e11270/2023-06/mickey1972330_339912340_544807387788244_5242588882259134988_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        孟耿如2020年嫁給黃子佼。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2678071/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼經常分享女兒的照片。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/07946caff2e71d7eef449fd766287643/2023-06/W16.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼經常分享女兒的照片。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2678072/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼經常分享女兒的照片。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc364bf8092064b80ec1e5e52c0c8201/2023-06/W17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼經常分享女兒的照片。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677995/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃子佼經常在社交網分享湊女的生活日常。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1314d21fa6fc94eda62bee0af75c2e80/2023-06/mickey1972330_343585508_162706660078342_4006332795046689749_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子佼經常在社交網分享湊女的生活日常。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/2677998/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"經常熱心公益，想不到原來表裡不一。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0770ee9589c10fcf3b73f8445aeafa26/2023-06/mickey1972330_354217071_10168109128440045_8146734796558151186_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        經常熱心公益，想不到原來表裡不一。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<h2>黃子佼毫無悔意</h2>\n<p>沈嶸通靈查詢黃子佼的腦波，從目前的黃子佼身上都沒有讀出「真心懺悔」的頻率，他的腦波中認為「這種東西很多人也有，我只是倒楣被人告發，才被檢警搜索到，不過是看點色情影片怎麼了嗎？」，可見他毫無悔意。\n\n</p><h2>黃子佼對自己財富很有自信</h2>\n<p>許多網友猜測黃子佼有想復出的想法，沈嶸通靈後表示，對於復出演藝圈他想都不敢想，也覺得應該不可行，但是對於在其它領域重新復出，他仍沒有放棄，正在尋找日後能發揮的地方，但目前還沒有定案。不過他也並不擔心，因為他對於自己的財富很有自信，自信自己錢一定夠用。\n\n</p><h2>黃子佼對曾國城有心結</h2>\n<p>另外，這次曾國城與徐乃麟聲援黃子佼的失言風波，沈嶸也通靈到黃子佼內心非常感謝徐乃麟為他仗義執言，但對同樣發聲的曾國城卻只有「部分感謝」，恐怕黃子佼對曾國城有心結。而去年4月沈嶸就曾通靈黃子佼「刑剋」孟耿如，會導致孟耿如的名聲受到牽連，事業路跟著受阻，只要孟耿如繼續跟黃子佼綁在一起，事業就不會有起色。\n\n</p><h2>黃子佼「惡業大爆發」</h2>\n<p>最後，沈嶸總結：「雖然以現今的法律無法讓黃子佼受到嚴厲的處罰，許多受害者看著他繼續安穩度過日常生活而感到憤怒、絕望，但根據靈界因果簿的記錄，黃子佼「惡業大爆發」還在持續當中，後面還有許多惡報等著他，天道必然會要他為自身的惡行付出代價，法官不予緩刑判8個月徒刑就是他的報應之一，未來等著他的惡事絕對遠不止於此。」\n\n</p>\n<p>【文章獲TVBS新聞網授權轉載】\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3315753/%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E4%BD%BC%E8%97%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%A3%B8%E9%9C%B2%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E9%87%8D%E5%88%A48%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%8D%B2%E6%80%A7%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%80%A7%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE-%E6%AF%80%E6%BB%85%E6%80%A7%E7%88%86%E6%96%99%E5%86%8D%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%98\">黃子佼藏少女裸露片被重判8個月 去年捲性醜聞遭網紅指控性騷擾 毀滅性爆料再自殘</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
